Package com.SuperheroSightings.springbootrestjdbctemplatemaven

Class HeroDAOImplTest

java.lang.Object
com.SuperheroSightings.springbootrestjdbctemplatemaven.HeroDAOImplTest
@ExtendWith(org.mockito.junit.jupiter.MockitoExtension.class) public class HeroDAOImplTest extends Object
Test class for the HeroDAOImpl. This class contains unit tests for the HeroDAOImpl using the JUnit 5 framework and Mockito for mocking dependencies. It ensures that the data access object for heroes performs its CRUD operations correctly.
